    title NESNet Character Movement Demo
  body
    .container
      .header.clearfix
        h3.text-muted NESNet Character Movement Demo
      .jumbotron
        h1 Move Around!
        p.lead
          | W/A/S/D will move your character around. This movement will be visible on your console, too.
        p
          .panel.panel-default.world
            .panel-body
        .row
          .col-md-4
            p
              | X: 
              span.p1PositionX
          .col-md-4
            p
              | Y: 
              span.p1PositionY
          .col-md-4
            p
              | Direction: 
              span.direction


